msgid "No layers were detected. You might want to repair your STL file(s) or check their size or thickness and retry.\n"
msgstr "Nebyly detekovány žádné vrstvy. Doporučujeme opravit svůj STL soubor či soubory, nebo zkontrolovat jejich velikost a tloušťku a poté to zkusit znovu.\n"

